*bibus-1.2.0 (17 Oct 2006)

  17 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; +metadata.xml,
  +bibus-1.2.0.ebuild:
  New package: Bibliographic and reference management software, integrates
  with OO.o and MS Word.

